  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Austria is a fairly quiet and traditional hotel which has recently undergone extensive refurbishments and now features a new reception and lobby area, a new dining room with house bar and a cosy cellar bar, which is a popular meeting place. The hotel is well known for its excellent food and friendly service.</p>
<p>Situated between <a data-udi="umb://document/0096e5e76c954be2b2a6b43d386098c6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0096e5e76c954be2b2a6b43d386098c6}" title="Saalbach">Saalbach</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/2d5ab9112aac4c73b620a816b632492b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2d5ab9112aac4c73b620a816b632492b}" title="Hinterglemm">Hinterglemm</a>, the ski bus stops outside the hotel and intermediate skiers can ski back to the hotel at the end of the day, weather permitting.</p>]]></description>
