  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Austria sits in a quiet location between <a data-udi="umb://document/5f1b95adea4b42b087ef6194cb7d5b06" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f1b95adea4b42b087ef6194cb7d5b06}" title="Skicircus Saalbach Hinterglemm Leogang Fieberbrunn">Saalbach and Hinterglemm</a>. The regular ski bus stops outside that will take you to either resort in less than five minutes. If the weather is on your side, you'll be able to ski back to the hotel from the mountain.</p>]]></listingDescription>
