  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Austrian Twins</strong> are around 25<span>m² and have a bath or shower and a seating area.</span></p>
<p><strong>Standard Triple Rooms</strong> are up to 28<span>m² and have a third single bed in addition to the main Austrian twin bed. These rooms also have a balcony.</span></p>
<p><strong>Standard Quad Rooms</strong> are 25-30<span>m² and sleep up to four. These rooms have an Austrian twin bed and an additional two single beds or bunks beds sleeping any third or fourth guests. Like the triple rooms, these also have a balcony.</span></p>]]></roomsDescription>
